#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_area2d.rst:170
msgid ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_DISABLED** = **0** --- This area does not affect "
"gravity/damping."
msgstr "**SPACE_OVERRIDE_DISABLED** = **0** —— 该区域不影响重力/阻尼。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_area2d.rst:172
msgid ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_COMBINE** = **1** --- This area adds its gravity/damping"
" values to whatever has been calculated so far (in :ref:`priority "
"<class_Area2D_property_priority>` order)."
msgstr ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_COMBINE** = **1** —— 该区域将其重力/阻尼值，添加到到目前为止已计算的任何值（按 "
":ref:`priority <class_Area2D_property_priority>` 的顺序）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_area2d.rst:174
msgid ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_COMBINE_REPLACE** = **2** --- This area adds its "
"gravity/damping values to whatever has been calculated so far (in "
":ref:`priority <class_Area2D_property_priority>` order), ignoring any "
"lower priority areas."
msgstr ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_COMBINE_REPLACE** = **2** —— "
"此区域将其重力/阻尼值，添加到到目前为止已计算的任何值（按 :ref:`priority "
"<class_Area2D_property_priority>` 的顺序），而忽略任何较低优先级的区域。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_area2d.rst:176
msgid ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_REPLACE** = **3** --- This area replaces any "
"gravity/damping, even the defaults, ignoring any lower priority areas."
msgstr "**SPACE_OVERRIDE_REPLACE** = **3** —— 该区域将替换所有重力/阻尼，甚至是默认设置，而忽略任何较低优先级的区域。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_area2d.rst:178
msgid ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_REPLACE_COMBINE** = **4** --- This area replaces any "
"gravity/damping calculated so far (in :ref:`priority "
"<class_Area2D_property_priority>` order), but keeps calculating the rest "
"of the areas."
msgstr ""
"**SPACE_OVERRIDE_REPLACE_COMBINE** = **4** —— 该区域替换了到目前为止，计算出的所有重力/阻尼（按 "
":ref:`priority <class_Area2D_property_priority>` 顺序），但仍在计算其余区域。"

